title: Infamous Casey Anthony Spotted Protesting at Trump’s Estate, Then People Make Stinging Observation…
text:
There is plenty to be embarrassed about if you’re a Democrat. 
But there was one person recently spotted at a Trump protest that might surprise you. 
Remember this face? 

A little strange right? 
The same people who are beating Americans who support Trump are totally cool with Casey Anthony being around? 
Here’s some feedback from Twitter. @NickCiletti @abc15 The same group who beat people in MAGA hats are fine with Casey Anthony. I do not understand. 
— Ginger McQuewn (@GingerMcQueen) February 5, 2017 This doesn't surprise me that the left has embraced #CaseyAnthony . After all, murdering babies is what they do. She's their new poster girl https://t.co/ReFFpAJNkt
